reviews.review_text:
Epic Show 😎 I met Dave in College at Syracuse University and he & another friend turned me on to the Dead and Taping shows. This show I decided not to tape as I was with my gf at the time and wanted to keep my attention on her & the music and not worry about taping as they still didn't have a taper's section yet. It's a bittersweet memory as she left me shortly after & moved to LA. I moved out to there in 83 but never got the relationship back. 
Buffalo 11/09/79 was my first Show & returning to Buffalo for this seemed like a full circle. I remember getting back to Cuse and getting a copy of this from his master's.
